-- CCB May Buy WestLB South American Assets, WSJ Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-05-09T13:44:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-09/ccb-may-buy-westlb-south-american-assets-wsj-reports.html
China Construction Bank Corp. (939)  is in
talks to buy the South American assets of WestLB AG, the Wall
Street Journal reported today, citing a person familiar with the
situation.  The bank seeks the assets to gain a foothold in commercial
banking in the continent in a deal that may be valued between
$200 million and $300 million and may be wrapped up by June, the
newspaper said.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
